@NODE HypAss_Introduction
@NEXT HypAss_Introduction
    HypAss is the "spider-monster" which connects all sections of a
    HyperSource© programming system, as there are:

            global configuration
            localization
            context sensitivity
            syntax libraries
            math libraries
            processor libraries
            object libraries
            action batch files

    And additionally you may also use it as an assembler ;-)


